    <description>This scheduled flow runs nightly to change Account Status from Active to Dormant if 

Update Dormant criteria to be as follows. If:

no activities logged in 90 days (emails and 3rd party app activities donâ€™t count as activities - use Date of Last Touch to ensure we are filtering out emails, highspot activity, LISN connection) requests, etc

AND - no jobs in 6 months 

AND - no active MSA 

AND - no MSA contract record status changes in 30 days (we do not currently track this)

Then Account should be Dormant.</description>
